---
title: Classic Surf and Steak Dinner with Tarragon Cream Sauce
description: This surf and turf dish is simple, saucy and crispy! Pan-seared steaks, smooth mashed potatoes and garlic shrimp are topped with a creamy sauce starring tarragon and Dijon mustard. They're the perfect partners-in-sauce!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/plat-terre-et-mer-classique-d99751f0.jpg
